SDG[0].comment: Apache Fineract supports the part of section 1.4 in the SDG-1 goals section, namely microfinance.

SDG[1].comment: Apache Fineract is concerned with providing financial tech to under-served populations. SDG 16's goal of strengthening institutions can imply stronger financial institutions but does not explicitly state it.

SDG[2].comment: Fineract promise of improved tech infrastructure can serve as an aid to improvements in tax collection and resource allocation.
